name: Kwame Adomako
profile_summary: This profile is for a 32-year-old man who is a Software Engineer in the technology industry. He stands tall at 6'1", is of Black African Descent, and primarily speaks English and Twi. He was educated at the University of Maryland and has completed his graduate studies. Originally from Silver Spring, Maryland, he is now dating in Los Angeles, California. His values include equality, creativity, education, and social justice and he enjoys coding, playing basketball, cooking, and photography. He's spiritual, politically liberal, and his intentions on the dating scene are geared towards a long-term, monogamous relationship. He is currently without children but wants them in the future. His preferred pronouns are he/him/his and identifies as straight. He does not smoke or use marijuana or drugs, but he does sometimes drink. He is quite active and exercises regularly. He does not have any pets, his zodiac sign is Taurus, and his MBTI personality type is INTJ.
